Started adding infrastructure for implementing MAS and environments

Implemented base environment class and base grid world model and view

Created MarsModel and MarsView
Added iterate method to perform one cycle of agent interpreter

Deleted commented lines (neatened class)

Started added actions including move and travel
Deleted max expression
Created IDE in FXML and implemented (1) load mas project, (2) tree view for file structure, (3) run project button

Commented printing to clean up text output

Updated agent file name
Added environment to executeAction(), executeIntention() methods.

Added different agents and update method

Added personal logger for each agent
Working on scenario

Implemented execution of test goal action to return a unifier, then subsitute it into the intended means for subsequent actions.
Moved goal variable from children to GoalAction class and deleted un-needed methods

Changed executeAction() to return unifier instead of boolean. It now returns the test goal unifier. The intended means executeAction() method now checks what type of action it is performing. If it is an achievement goal then it makes subgoalFlag=true

All executeAction() methods return the unifier they are passed except for test goals. The intended means executeAction() method now sets the subgoal flag and then has one call to action.executeAction() that returns a unifier which is set to be the intended means unifier.
Added folder icon to git
Initial belief cant be atom anymore. Test goals are now formulas and not terms
Added MASProject parser files to git
Added check for number type (IntNum od DoubleNum) and convert to double as appropriate.

Corrected unification for a structure with a structure

Reduced entails methods for negations into one. Reduced entails methods for relational expressions into one.
Corrected return of getWeight(negativeLiteral). Simplified getLambda(Disjunction) to a Math.min
Added getLamda() methods for contradiction and tautology methods.

Added min and mac get weight functions. Corrected getLambda(BeliefLiteral) method. It didn't add the belief literal to the set of bounded literals. Deleted getLambda() methods for conjunction and disjunctions
Added logger which writes to separate files for each agent
Changed use of convertToNNF and use .equal instaed of != in pare for NotEqual

Added apache-log4j binaries
Editing environment for 9 locations scenario
